Comment: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fn方正FW珍珠体 简繁\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(970,740)}不滅的三戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.99,Default,cht,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H0水20103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(970,740)}不滅的三戰士
Comment: 0,0:24:53.02,0:24:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs100\fsp15\fn方正FW珍珠体 简繁\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(970,740)}想要守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.02,0:24:56.02,Default,cht,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(970,740)}想要守護的東西
